  "text": "However, [CITATION_1] did not investigate the relation that the identified organizational characteristics have to the ISFAM, or the influence these organizational characteristics have on information security in a quantitative measure. This research attempts to deploy these organizational characteristics on the ISFAM, and understand the influence the organizational characteristics have on focus areas within the ISFAM. Furthermore it will present an adaptive ISFAM as a proof-of-concept for adaptive maturity matrices.",
  "correct_citation": {
